$interpreted: PAFF: Ah, I'm still...in that world...
PAFF: I remember now. We were attacked by monsters.
PAFF: Then I fell down from...
PAFF: ...A-All in all, I have to meet up with them as soon as possible.
PAFF: How did this end up here? Isn't this suppose to be a different world...
PAFF: ...Don't be scared, Aroma! You need to find them fast!
PAFF: Come on...don't be nervous...you can do it!
PAFF: ...Remember those feelings I had before I took the stage...
PAFF: (Wha...what do I do now? W-why won't he leave?)
PAFF: H-hello, sorry for disturbing you...

PAFF: I'll leave right away...
P......Please don't attack me...
PAFF: Does this mean...you want to listen to me sing?

PAFF: If you like my singing...
Then...how about I sing one more song for you?
PAFF: Thank you...for liking my music so much.
PAFF: I'm sorry...If I can, I would've loved to keep singing for you too. However, I must go now...They must be worried sick about me.
PAFF: Why are you still following me?
PAFF: Could it be, that you also got separated from your friends?
PAFF: Turns out you're the same as me...
PAFF: If that's the case, how about we...go together?
PAFF: So your name is "Garu"? What a cute-sounding name~
PAFF: Well then, Garu...it's a real pleasure.
